  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Because we don't distinguish inbound or outbound peer in \"peer:connect\" we send status request if we are dealer or receiver. According to spec we should only send status request if we are dialer. We should probably additionally emit \"peer:inbound:connected\" and \"peer:outbound:connected\" and only send status request if we encouter later event",
